name: Vessels 119: Story Beat 004
description:
6) Henry opens his eyes, anger flaring.
HENRY: I DID PROMISE.  THEN YOU DIDN’T TURN UP FOR WORK WHEN YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO. I CAN’T ASK THE WHOLE CREW TO STAND AROUND DOING NOTHING FOR HOURS ONEND WHILE YOU CATCH UP ON YOUR BEAUTY SLEEP. YOUR BROTHER WAS HERE AND YOU WEREN’T. END OF STORY.
7) Angle on Betsy as she lowers her head so she doesn’t have to meet Henry’s disapproving gaze. If her eyes were glowing they are no longer doing so.
